<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
	<div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
		<div class="modal-content modal-howwechoose">
			<div class="modal-header">
				<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
				<h1 class="modal-title text-center" id="myModalLabel">How we choose</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="modal-body">
				<div class="containter-fluid">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<div class="well well-icon text-center">
								<img src="../assets/icon_hwc-step1.png" alt="icon_hwc-step1" width="170" height="170" class="img-responsive center-block"/>
								<p>We rate all physicians based on factors that demonstrate clinical excellence such as patient outcomes, training, research, hospital affiliation, and procedure volumes.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<div class="well well-icon text-center">
								<img src="../assets/icon_hwc-step2.png" alt="icon_hwc-step2" width="170" height="170" class="img-responsive center-block"/>
								<p>We then find the top physicians that are located near you, accept your insurance, and satisfy any personal preferences.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4">
							<div class="well well-icon text-center">
								<img src="../assets/icon_hwc-step3.png" alt="icon_hwc-step3" width="170" height="170" class="img-responsive center-block"/>
								<p>Finally, your Staff Physician, a licensed doctor, will hand pick the specialist that best matches your needs.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
